    • Method Detail

      • collide

        public void collide(city.cs.engine.CollisionEvent e)
        Checks for collision with an enemy, player and a box. If collided with an enemy, create a corner object if not already created. If collided with a player, set the player in a new position. If collided with a box, set the box in a new position. If collision with the bottom wall or top wall, reverse and revert gravity respectively.
        Specified by:
        collide in interface city.cs.engine.CollisionListener
